stickerText:
H0e phase? 
Not this good girl.

Never met a mom who didn’t love me or who’s son hasn’t called “wife only material” since college. 

Has checked every box every youth group pastor, cotillion instructor or “the rules” book has ever thrown at me with flying colors. 

No ring on my finger despite it. No prospects for anyone to make it past date 3 if we’re being honest. And now most of my friends are not only one life stage past me but two (although I don’t envy infant life, it looks brutal).

WHAT?
